@node Poke Architecture
@chapter Poke Architecture

PCL stands for ``Poke Control Language'', and also for ``Poke C-like
Language''.  It is pronounced ``pickle''.

@verbatim

      +----------+
      | compiler |
      +----------+
           |
           v
      +----------+      +-------+
      |   PVM    | <--->|       |
      +----------+      |       |
           ^            |       |
           |            | data  |
           v            |       |
      +----------+      |       |
      | command  | <--->|       |
      +----------+      +-------+

@end verbatim

Files:

@table @file
@item pcl.h
PCL compiler header file.
@item pcl-ast.h pcl-ast.c
PCL abstract syntax tree.
@item pcl-gen.c
PCL code generator.
@item pcl-lex.l pcl-lex.y
PCL parser and lexer.
@item pvm.h pvm.c
Poke virtual machine.
@end table

